ysis. There are also substantial sections on word order, stylistics, and figures of speech. Translations are provided for almost all passages "ed. The work will be welcomed by Iranianists as well as by historical linguists with wider Indo-European interests.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aAvestan languagexSyntax. 4aAltavestisch. 4aIndogermanische Sprachen. 4aZarathustra. 4airanische Sprache. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aIndo-European Languages.  aIranian Language.  aOld Avestan.  aZarathushtra.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2011z9783110261189oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET PHILOSOPHIE UND GESCHICHTE 2011z9783110261257oZDB-23-DGE0 cprintz978311025308540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311025309240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110253092423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110253092/original  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGEb2011  aZDB-23-DGGb2011  aZDB-23-DLSc2000d2014